metadata.shopMessage: **Vibrant and Colourful** or Muted and Dark? Choose from a variety of amazing icon designs by the best creators out there! There is something available for everyone. Most icon packs include alternatives and icon overlays. Use ShowAE to apply them!
metadata.shortcutsMessage:
**Explore** the Show shortcuts below. ShowLive & ShowLive Helper shortcuts are required to install themes with this app. Install and setup ShowLive first before downloading themes.

Shorcut versions are for **iOS 15.1 and higher**. See our Discord server for other versions.
metadata.howToMessage:
**Follow our tutorials** and learn how to select, download and apply themes with ShowLive. We cover everything to get you started with easy to follow videos and detailed step by step written instructions.

For further support visit our Discord server. Link at the bottom of this page.

metadata.downloadInstructionsMessage:
#Once download completes:

The iOS share sheet will appear. Tap on **ShowLive Helper** to install the theme.

You can then choose to run the ShowLive shortcut to apply the theme on your device, or choose exit if you plan to apply the theme later
